mething more out of atomic rockets. railguns and space capable missiles, not blasters and photon torpedoes.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222017-01-30T00:51:03Z\u0022 title=\u002201/30/2017 12:51  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EJanuary 30, 2017\u003C/time\u003E by toric5\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"SpannerMonkey(smce)","CreatedById":50907,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-30T00:51:55Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222938652\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022155014\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221485737433\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002258046\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022toric5\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nJust now, toric5 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\ni mean to sci fi as in physically unplausible, technobabble, star wars and star trek. i would be looking for something more out of atomic rockets. railguns and space capable missiles, not blasters and photon torpedoes.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFair enough, a valid point I s\u0027pose, I\u0027ll think on it a bit\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}